lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 17:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/two-seat-variant-of-russias-su-57-felon-fighter-materializes</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰本土滑翔炸弹突破掩护</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-homegrown-glide-bomb-breaks-cover</link><description>&lt;p&gt;乌克兰迫切需要额外的空射防区外弹药，特别是不受外国供应链和使用限制的弹药。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-homegrown-glide-bomb-breaks-cover"&gt;乌克兰本土滑翔炸弹突破掩护的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 May 2026 16:49:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ukraines-homegrown-glide-bomb-breaks-cover</guid></item></channel></rss>